Somebody say I'm crowned with love and kindness and tender mercies.

41:10.528 --> 41:11.809
That's how we should be walking.

41:12.430 --> 41:12.610
Amen?

41:12.990 --> 41:24.562
We should be crowned with love and kindness and tender mercies who satisfies our mouth with good things so that our youth is renewed like the Eagles.

41:24.602 --> 41:26.443
How many people are confessing that on a daily basis?

41:26.844 --> 41:28.185
Especially your older people out here.

41:28.245 --> 41:28.526
Amen?

41:28.906 --> 41:33.170
My youth is renewed like the Eagles

41:33.410 --> 41:39.399
And it says here that Lord, execute righteous and justice for all who are oppressed.

41:40.020 --> 41:47.552
So if we focus and we stay focused, what keeps us in praise and worship is focusing on what Jesus has done for us.

41:47.592 --> 42:00.351
And when you have that heart of praise and worship and thankfulness that cultivates a heart of love for God and that heart of love for God will penetrate our souls to love others.

42:00.952 --> 42:02.034
Do you believe that today?

42:02.242 --> 42:08.972
When we are really loving God and you're in a beautiful relationship with the Lord, your relationship should be good too.

42:10.194 --> 42:13.078
Because it should be good vertically and horizontally.

42:13.739 --> 42:17.185
If it's good with your relationship with God, it should be good with your relationship with others.

42:17.966 --> 42:21.030
But if it's bad with your relationship with God, it's going to be bad with others.

42:22.392 --> 42:22.713
Amen.

42:22.753 --> 42:27.420
If you're in sin, doing the wrong things, your relationship is going to be wrecked.

42:28.382 --> 42:31.346
Because sin separates us from the love of God.

42:31.842 --> 42:41.597
So in closing, if you're gonna walk in the love of God, we gotta walk in the love of God by being selfless and not selfish.

42:42.338 --> 42:48.027
If we're gonna walk in the love of God, God's love will compel us to be givers.

42:48.768 --> 42:55.438
If we're gonna walk in the love of God, it will motivate us to show love and mercy and forgive those that offend us.

42:56.079 --> 42:58.002
If we're gonna walk in God's love,

42:58.242 --> 43:01.711
It will prop us to worship and give thanks to God.

43:01.731 --> 43:09.952
And if we're going to walk in God's love, we will demonstrate it by remembering what Jesus has done for us.

43:10.614 --> 43:13.842
And I'm telling you, when you start focusing on what Jesus

43:13.986 --> 43:20.777
has done for you, your love, and it's gonna compel you to be a bold witness for Christ.

43:21.218 --> 43:25.265
You're gonna tell people about how good God has been for you.

43:25.325 --> 43:33.479
And I'm telling you, you're gonna draw people into the love of God and bring them into the salvation of the Lord, amen?

43:33.880 --> 43:35.302
Did you receive it this morning?

43:35.743 --> 43:36.905
I believe you did, amen?

43:36.965 --> 43:40.050
We're gonna walk in love if the hair lifts the devil, amen?

